text: Enicodes fichteli is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Schreibers in 1902. It is known from New Caledonia and Australia.BioLib.cz - Enicodes fichteli. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1902
